{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"m9u70yufp50mimd6jg9k5o7","title":"Patterns","desc":"","updated":1663657672812,"created":1658656908100,"custom":{},"fname":"areas.gamedev.dragonruby.patterns","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","name":"digital-garden","selfContained":true},"contentHash":"50e965beb6821e51c7ff9d3975b7cfea","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"areas.gamedev.dragonruby.patterns","id":"m9u70yufp50mimd6jg9k5o7","vaultName":"digital-garden"},"value":"areas.gamedev.dragonruby.patterns.input-actions","alias":"Input Actions","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":4,"offset":36},"end":{"line":3,"column":69,"offset":101},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"areas.gamedev.dragonruby.patterns.input-actions"}},{"type":"ref","from":{"fname":"areas.gamedev.dragonruby.patterns","id":"m9u70yufp50mimd6jg9k5o7","vaultName":"digital-garden"},"value":"areas.gamedev.dragonruby.patterns.input-actions","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1,"offset":102},"end":{"line":4,"column":93,"offset":194},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"areas.gamedev.dragonruby.patterns.input-actions","anchorHeader":"input-actions,1:#background--principles"}}],"anchors":{"patterns-to-use-in-dragonruby":{"type":"header","text":"Patterns to use in DragonRuby","value":"patterns-to-use-in-dragonruby","line":7,"column":0,"depth":1},"input-actions":{"type":"header","text":"Input Actions","value":"input-actions","line":9,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["dr-patterns-input-actions"],"parent":"2fdt0zsteynlm6ax8wr7k3x","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"patterns-to-use-in-dragonruby\">Patterns to use in DragonRuby<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#patterns-to-use-in-dragonruby\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"input-actions\"><a href=\"/digital-garden/notes/dr-patterns-input-actions\">Input Actions</a><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#input-actions\"></a></h2>\n<p></p><p></p><div class=\"portal-container\">\n<div class=\"portal-head\">\n<div class=\"portal-backlink\">\n<div class=\"portal-title\">From <span class=\"portal-text-title\">Input Actions</span></div>\n<a href=\"/digital-garden/notes/dr-patterns-input-actions\" class=\"portal-arrow\">Go to text <span class=\"right-arrow\">â†’</span></a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"portal-parent-anchor\" class=\"portal-parent\" markdown=\"1\">\n<div class=\"portal-parent-fader-top\"></div>\n<div class=\"portal-parent-fader-bottom\"></div><p>Instead of using <code>args.inputs</code> directly you parse it into an input actions objects, which is then used instead to\ncontrol your game.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/digital-garden/./assets/images/input_actions.png\" alt=\"Input Actions\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"when-is-it-useful\">When is it useful?<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#when-is-it-useful\"></a></h2>\n<p>Some scenarios when this pattern can be useful:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Having several different kinds of inputs with the same effect</li>\n<li>Configurable controls</li>\n<li>Letting an AI player control your game (character)</li>\n<li>Multiplayer</li>\n</ul>\n<p>In general I think it results in cleaner, better organized code but YMMV of course.</p>\n</div></div><p></p><p></p>\n<hr>\n<strong>Children</strong>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"/digital-garden/notes/dr-patterns-input-actions\">Input Actions</a></li>\n</ol>","noteIndex":{"id":"w4mxpqpj9ftyo6pw17k3wj6","title":"Home","desc":"","updated":1660372010574,"created":1648806032875,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","name":"digital-garden","selfContained":true},"contentHash":"0d5b5a84c07edaf83aeeab9a0b1a2b42","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"w4mxpqpj9ftyo6pw17k3wj6","vaultName":"digital-garden"},"value":"contact_me","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":55,"offset":331},"end":{"line":10,"column":69,"offset":345},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"contact_me"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"r